comments: Abolished 30.9.1900 and added to the parish of Hertford.

Abolished 1894 to become the separate parishes of Bengeo Urban 
    and Bengeo Rural.

Abolished 1894 to become the separate parishes of Brickendon Urban 
    and Brickendon Rural.

Abolished 1894 to become the separate parishes of St. Andrew Urban 
    and St. Andrew Rural.

Abolished 1894 and divided between the parishes of St. John Urban 
    and St. John Rural.
